task.summary: Separate stats functions into python. Add DVARS to main script.
Add orthoslice movie generation (cbicqalive.py) for qualitative temporal noise assessments.
Separate batch and individual scripts. Refactor quality assurance (QA) to quality control (QC) throughout, including project name
Corrected run condition for temporary scripts. Removed PDF report generation
Forced matplot to use Agg backend without X server. Fixed qc_info.csv loading for report.
Fixed info parsing for HTML report. Now using summary info including stats in qc_info.csv
Fixed correct escape of loop variable in summary script
Fixed correct escape of loop variable in summary script
Set sensible directory name defaults for cbicqclive_batch (dicom, source)
Divide brain mask into inner and outer ROIs by erosion of whole brain mask (20 mm radius). Take median tSFNR within inner and outer ROIs for report.
Refactored mask image filenames for clarity. Added phantom/invivo flag for signal mask generation (simple vs BET).
